    • User

      public User(String name, String email, String phoneNumber, String uniqueId, boolean isOrganizer, boolean isEntrant, Facility facility, boolean notificationStatus, String colour, ArrayList<String> entrantEventList, ArrayList<String> organizerEventList, boolean isAdmin)
      Contructor method for the User class, creates a User object
      Parameters:
      name - the user's name
      email - the user's email
      phoneNumber - the user's phone number
      uniqueId - the user's id, used to identify them in Firebase
      isOrganizer - a boolean representing if the user is an organizer
      isEntrant - a boolean representing if the user is an entrant
      facility - a facility object associated with the user
      notificationStatus - a boolean representing if the user has notifications turned on
      colour - a string representing the background colour for a user's avatar
      entrantEventList - a list of events that our user has joined
      organizerEventList - a list of events the user has made
      isAdmin - a boolean representing if the user is an admin
